{"article_id":"9dBKm19UZuMzk7os","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"JERUSALEM , Israel -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Exit polls indicate","depth":9},{"id":2,"text":"that Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu has beaten rival Blue and White Party leader Benny Gantz ,","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"but it is unclear if he will secure enough seats","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"to have a parliamentary majority","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"and guarantee another term in office .","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"Jubilation erupted at Likud party headquarters Monday evening","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"as exit polls streamed in","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"revealing","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"that Netanyahu had defeated Gantz .","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"\" It 's a win against all odds","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"because we stood up against powerful forces .","depth":13},{"id":12,"text":"They already eulogized us .","depth":13},{"id":13,"text":"Our enemies said ,","depth":14},{"id":14,"text":"' The Netanyahu era is over. '","depth":14},{"id":15,"text":"But we turned the plate on its head , \"","depth":13},{"id":16,"text":"Netanyahu told a crowd of supporters ,","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"adding","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"that it is \" the biggest win of my life . \"","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"Netanyahu ' s right-wing bloc is on track to win at least 59 seats in Israel ' s 120-seat parliament , just short of the 61 seats","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"he needs","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"to form a governing majority .","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"Still , Likud issued a devastating blow to Blue and White .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"Pollsters predicted","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"that the two parties would be neck-in-neck after the third election","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"and unable to break through a nearly year-long political deadlock .","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"But Netanyahu ' s surge in seats gives him a decisive advantage over Gantz ,","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"who is projected to win 32 seats .","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"Netanyahu ' s next task is to form a majority government coalition .","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"If he fails ,","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"Israel will be on track for a fourth election .","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"However , his supporters believe","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"this time he wo n't be denied .","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"Still , Gantz refused to concede ,","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"opting to wait","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"until every vote is counted","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"before accepting defeat .","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"\" We created something","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"called Blue and White .","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"We merged our documents and principles to one place","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"and I am telling you","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"that we wo n't compromise on our principles and our way , \"","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"Gantz said Monday night .","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"In past campaigns , Likud counted on former defense minister Avigdor Liberman as a solid part of the right-wing bloc .","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"But he started the election stalemate last year","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"after refusing to join a government with Likud ' s ultra-orthodox allies ,","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"who are not Zionists","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"and refuse to serve in the military .","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"Liberman is head of the secular nationalist Yisrael Beiteinu Party ,","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"which won about seven seats .","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"On Tuesday , Liberman maintained","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"his role as the kingmaker","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"who could give Netanyahu the seats","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"needs to form a government ,","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"but Liberman says","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"he wo n't compromise .","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"`` We will not join any government","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"led by","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"[ Prime Minister Benjamin ] Netanyahu","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"that includes Shas and United Torah Judaism","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"( ultra-orthodox parties ) , \"","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"Liberman tweeted .","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"Even if Gantz and Liberman wo n't compromise ,","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"the Likud camp believes","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"in the coming days","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"they can find Knesset members from the left or the center","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"to join them ,","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"and save Israelis from a fourth election .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"Israel will not have final election results until Thursday ,","depth":4},{"id":69,"text":"after soldiers , diplomats , and those in mandatory coronavirus quarantine have their votes counted .","depth":4},{"id":70,"text":"Netanyahu hopes","depth":5},{"id":71,"text":"a potential parliamentary majority will give him the power and protection","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"he wants","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"to fight the corruption charges against him .","depth":6},{"id":74,"text":"Netanyahu is charged with bribery , fraud and breach of trust ,","depth":5},{"id":75,"text":"although he maintains his innocence .","depth":5},{"id":76,"text":"His trial will begin on March 17","depth":4},{"id":77,"text":"but he hopes to clinch together a government majority before then .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":155,"left":0,"right":154,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":154,"left":146,"right":153,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":146,"left":144,"right":145,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":144,"left":119,"right":143,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":119,"left":104,"right":118,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":95,"right":103,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":95,"left":82,"right"